a.xlink:title: Emma, tell me a joke about goldfish and peanut butter.

Here's one:
So I was at the pet store buying some food for my goldfish, and I saw they had this special "goldfish-sized" jar of peanut butter. And I'm thinking, "Is that really a thing? Do fish even like peanut butter?" But then I thought, "Hey, it can't be worse than the time I tried to teach him how to do tricks for a Froot Loop!"
Your turn, Jack!
